      "expectedAnswer": "Issues: 1) Incorrect Layer Ordering, 2) Direct UI to Database connection. Corrected: Presentation -> Business -> Data Access -> Database."
    },
    {
      "id": "Q3",
      "description": "Identifying Bounded Contexts (DDD)",
      "points": 8,
      "questionType": "text-only",
      "keyConcepts": ["bounded context", "domain-driven design", "entities"],
      "expectedAnswer": "Bounded Contexts: 1) Booking Context - Ticket booking. 2) Flight Management - Schedules. 3) Payment Context - Payments. 4) User Management - Users and roles."
    }
